<article class="text">
	<header>
		<h1>Formulários</h1>
		<h2>Tipos de campos de formulários.</h2>
	</header>

	<p>Veja abaixo alguns exemplos e as variações de campos de formulários que podemos usar.</p>

	<h3>Campos suportados</h3>
	<p>
		O locastyle da suporte a todas as variações de campos de formulário em HTML5, como:
		<code>text</code>, <code>password</code>, <code>datetime</code>, <code>datetime-local</code>, <code>date</code>, <code>month</code>, <code>time</code>, <code>week</code>, <code>number</code>, <code>email</code>, <code>url</code>, <code>search</code>, <code>tel</code>, e <code>color</code>.
	</p>
	<div class="example">
		<form>
			<input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Input de texto">
		</form>
	</div>
	<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; placeholder=&quot;Input de texto&quot;&gt;</pre>
	<h3>Textarea</h3>
	<p>Você pode alterar o parâmetro <code>rows</code> se for necessário.</p>
	<div class="example">
		<form>
			<textarea class="form-control" rows="3"></textarea>
		</form>
	</div>
	<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">&lt;textarea class=&quot;form-control&quot; rows=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;</pre>

	<h3>Checkboxes e Radio Buttons</h3>
	<p>Para selecionar <strong>mais de 1</strong> opção utilize os <code>checkboxes</code>, para selecionar <strong>apenas 1</strong> utilize o <code>radio buttons</code></p>
	<div class="example">
		<form>
			<div class="checkbox">
				<input type="checkbox" value="" id="checkbox-1">
				<label for="checkbox-1">Marque aqui</label>
			</div>
			<div class="checkbox">
				<input type="checkbox" value="" id="checkbox-2">
				<label for="checkbox-2">E marque aqui também</label>
			</div>

			<div class="radio">
				<input type="radio" name="optionsRadios" id="optionsRadios1" value="option1" checked>
				<label for="optionsRadios1">Ou marque aqui</label>
			</div>
			<div class="radio">
				<input type="radio" name="optionsRadios" id="optionsRadios2" value="option2">
				<label for="optionsRadios2">Ou marque aqui</label>
			</div>
		</form>
	</div>
	<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;div class=&quot;checkbox&quot;&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; value=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;checkbox-1&quot;&gt;
	&lt;label for=&quot;checkbox-1&quot;&gt;Marque aqui&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;checkbox&quot;&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; value=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;checkbox-2&quot;&gt;
	&lt;label for=&quot;checkbox-2&quot;&gt;E marque aqui tamb&#xe9;m&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;radio&quot;&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;optionsRadios&quot; id=&quot;optionsRadios1&quot; value=&quot;option1&quot; checked&gt;
	&lt;label for=&quot;optionsRadios1&quot;&gt;Ou marque aqui&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;radio&quot;&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;optionsRadios&quot; id=&quot;optionsRadios2&quot; value=&quot;option2&quot;&gt;
	&lt;label for=&quot;optionsRadios2&quot;&gt;Ou marque aqui&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</pre>
	<h4>Checkboxes e Radio Buttons em linha</h4>
	<p>Utilize as classes <code>.checkbox-inline</code> ou <code>.radio-inline</code> para alinhar os elementos na horizontal.</p>
	<div class="example">
		<form>
			<label class="checkbox-inline">
	<input type="checkbox" id="inlineCheckbox1" value="option1"> 1
</label>
<label class="checkbox-inline">
	<input type="checkbox" id="inlineCheckbox2" value="option2"> 2
</label>
<label class="checkbox-inline">
	<input type="checkbox" id="inlineCheckbox3" value="option3"> 3
</label>
		</form>
	</div>
	<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;label class=&quot;checkbox-inline&quot;&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; id=&quot;inlineCheckbox1&quot; value=&quot;option1&quot;&gt; 1
&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;label class=&quot;checkbox-inline&quot;&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; id=&quot;inlineCheckbox2&quot; value=&quot;option2&quot;&gt; 2
&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;label class=&quot;checkbox-inline&quot;&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; id=&quot;inlineCheckbox3&quot; value=&quot;option3&quot;&gt; 3
&lt;/label&gt;</pre>

	<h3>Seletores</h3>
	<p>Use a opção padrão ou adicione o parâmetro <code>multiple</code></p>
	<div class="example">
		<select class="form-control">
			<option>1</option>
			<option>2</option>
			<option>3</option>
			<option>4</option>
			<option>5</option>
		</select>
		<br>
		<select multiple class="form-control">
			<option>1</option>
			<option>2</option>
			<option>3</option>
			<option>4</option>
			<option>5</option>
		</select>
	</div>
	<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;select class=&quot;form-control&quot;&gt;
	&lt;option&gt;1&lt;/option&gt;
	&lt;option&gt;2&lt;/option&gt;
	&lt;option&gt;3&lt;/option&gt;
	&lt;option&gt;4&lt;/option&gt;
	&lt;option&gt;5&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;/select&gt;

&lt;select multiple class=&quot;form-control&quot;&gt;
	&lt;option&gt;1&lt;/option&gt;
	&lt;option&gt;2&lt;/option&gt;
	&lt;option&gt;3&lt;/option&gt;
	&lt;option&gt;4&lt;/option&gt;
	&lt;option&gt;5&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;/select&gt;</pre>
